    "To inform decision-making, automated monitoring, and evaluation of individual components and overall performance will be essential.",
    "These data will provide valuable feedback to refine the system, mitigate risks, and address limitations effectively.",
    "This study had several strengths.",
    "Primarily, we included a large number of patients with coded inclusion and exclusion criteria ascertained previously by study staff and an expert clinician.",
    "Second, the extensive dataset used is derived from an ongoing randomized clinical trial, which is particularly valuable as it provides a rich, authentic context for applying and evaluating GPT-4 in clinical trial screening, ensuring that the findings are grounded in practical, real-world scenarios."
